AnyDVD HD decodes your movies on DVD, daring even to those recorded in protected DVD.

AnyDVD HD works in the background, running in the background in real time, without having to copy or extract data to hard disk, and makes the film appear "free", ie without protection, and no region code (" region code free ").

Thus, with AnyDVD HD you can make copies of your movies on DVD and Blu-Ray even if they are protected and can play any DVD, even of a different region that will support your system.

AnyDVD HD supports HD DVD and Blu-Ray.
